   at Microsoft.Exchange.Management.ExoPowershellSnapin.NewExoPSSession.ProcessRecord() in C:\git\migration\exchange\PSModuleCore\ExoPowerShellModule\NewExoPSSession.cs:line 300
   at System.Management.Automation.Cmdlet.DoProcessRecord()
   at System.Management.Automation.CommandProcessor.ProcessRecord()
